---
import ArchiveTimeline from '../../components/ArchiveTimeline.astro';
import { careerItems } from '../../data/site';
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Career - Jay Lee"
  description="Jay Lee's public résumé-level timeline across HRD, AI education, data, communication, and business."
>
  <section class="section page-hero">
    <div class="section-header compact-header">
      <h1>Career & Education</h1>
      <p>
        The public outline of where I have worked and studied. It explains the background behind the tools without turning
        internal work into portfolio material.
      </p>
    </div>
    <h2 class="sr-only">Career timeline</h2>
    <ArchiveTimeline items={careerItems} label="Career and education timeline" />
  </section>

  <section class="section compact-section language-band">
    <p>The thread across the timeline is learning: how people build capability, how organizations change, and how data and AI can help without removing judgment.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
